# Kerwizzy's LIVE Code Demos
*Live Demos don't bite*

Try out some live demos, such as:

[HTML5 Fractal Renderer](kerwizzy.github.io/FractalRenderer.html)

- Zoomings
 - Zoom in to 10,000,000,000,000,000 times magnification!
 - Easy to use interface
- Many Fractals!
 - Mandelbrot Set
 - Burning Ship Fractal
 - Mandelbar
- Fancy color palettes!
 - Royal, Frost, Fire, Grassland, and More!
- Reusable!
 - Can change code to render lots of fractals
